{"tid":321650,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一個好既旅伴真係好撚重要","createTime":"2017-07-14T10:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T17:44:33.000Z","uid":32927,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1741d35257dd418ed2b58b060ff37ae4080bb29b","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:04:45.000Z","msg":"要搵到一個同自己夾既人一齊去旅行真係好撚難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同個港女老母去旅行慘撚到食屎 又唔可以唔陪佢去<br />\n屌你出發前一日乜柒都唔執 ok算我幫你執埋 <br />\n去到東京喇 咁東京啲電梯就左企右行 佢就繼續我行我素企返右邊 係唔撚理人地既文化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢到都未係重點<br />\n咁7月去得旅行都預撚左貴 咁我就book左間hkd$700左右係既酒店 咁佢就要求方便既 我呢間係新宿附近 呢個價位算平 一去到酒店又即刻嫌三嫌四 話唔靚又細乜乜柒柒 屌你呢個價呢個location仲想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢照相又影撚極都唔滿意 屌鳩我影到佢柒 陪佢shopping又乜柒都我拎 朝早又唔願起身 真係正宗港女黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去7日東京 第1日已經想返香港 同佢去簡直係ruin左成個trip<br />\n之前同個fd去又係好撚慘 廢事太長轉頭再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人有類似經驗分享下"},{"pid":"2164fe1d5653893461bcdf9028af7f9f02cdf00b","tid":321650,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:07:10.000Z","msg":"你勁<br />\n我去親啲friend都無咩問題 好隨和<br />\n係有時玩手機太勁唔理我比我屌左次<br />\n家人更加冇事 食好住好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2054204b1a598b39e8500418a6b0d8a66caf493f","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你勁<br />\n我去親啲friend都無咩問題 好隨和<br />\n係有時玩手機太勁唔理我比我屌左次<br />\n家人更加冇事 食好住好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去親啲fd都好撚有問題"},{"pid":"454502a847057658b8a1f0a397463bcf6f24a5e1","tid":321650,"uid":30272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你勁<br />\n我去親啲friend都無咩問題 好隨和<br />\n係有時玩手機太勁唔理我比我屌左次<br />\n家人更加冇事 食好住好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去親啲fd都好撚有問題</blockquote><br />\n會唔會問題係你度？"},{"pid":"faaa5df5f2feef434ea947b1239041e99fe3a2a1","tid":321650,"uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"同年紀大啲既親戚去都預左比佢地嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本又嫌 台灣又嫌 東南亞又嫌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我學醒左 帶佢地玩啲大陸三日兩夜果啲團 佢地反而玩得好開心<br />\n<br />\n不過家人都唔係問題 如果預著同另一半個旅行方式唔岩仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb45b9426ea29a33eb1aea6abe53a1e6f833e63b","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:16:39.000Z","msg":"講埋同我去旅行既其中一個fd<br />\n慳住去旅行係ok 但佢係慳撚到我一日淨食得一餐正餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返到香港我係瘦左 但仲要係咁陪佢食啲濕鳩pancake 食左最少3-4次 又貴又難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前試過2對情侶去旅行(同一個fd黎) 都唔撚知係咪趕住返去扑野 日日都7pm左右就返酒店 又係唔撚肯坐低食正餐 日撚日都掃街 掃你老母咩 全撚部都係差唔多既野食 洗唔洗日撚日都掃 你掃1-2日咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2對情侶去以為會好玩過同佢兩條友去啦 點知好撚on9 一齊plan完冇一日係跟行程 完全分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 重點係佢地r我同我男朋友一齊去先 每一日我都要透過sc/ ig先知佢地去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係wtsapp單聲佢地去左邊"},{"pid":"66daf5532d99a4e8b03f178bc170b13b6e263128","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你勁<br />\n我去親啲friend都無咩問題 好隨和<br />\n係有時玩手機太勁唔理我比我屌左次<br />\n家人更加冇事 食好住好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去親啲fd都好撚有問題</blockquote><br />\n會唔會問題係你度？</blockquote><br />\n可能啦 唔知"},{"pid":"1f45cbd38f1cef30f6c6297c3cfee23e4038eed1","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:17:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同年紀大啲既親戚去都預左比佢地嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本又嫌 台灣又嫌 東南亞又嫌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我學醒左 帶佢地玩啲大陸三日兩夜果啲團 佢地反而玩得好開心<br />\n<br />\n不過家人都唔係問題 如果預著同另一半個旅行方式唔岩仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好彩同男朋友旅行方式係幾夾"},{"pid":"d6317fa4406a83749e0c431bee7c337827e2b408","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:18:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你勁<br />\n我去親啲friend都無咩問題 好隨和<br />\n係有時玩手機太勁唔理我比我屌左次<br />\n家人更加冇事 食好住好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我去親啲fd都好撚有問題</blockquote><br />\n會唔會問題係你度？</blockquote><br />\n可能啦 唔知</blockquote><br />\nBetween唔係同過好多人去過旅行既咁又"},{"pid":"6430ae33a8bae91f4181f1cf25afd8ed0aab0c86","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同年紀大啲既親戚去都預左比佢地嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本又嫌 台灣又嫌 東南亞又嫌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我學醒左 帶佢地玩啲大陸三日兩夜果啲團 佢地反而玩得好開心<br />\n<br />\n不過家人都唔係問題 如果預著同另一半個旅行方式唔岩仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同老母講之前上網睇到話日本人都唔多鍾意香港遊客 我老母話咩咁咪好似啲香港人會歧視啲內地同胞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係帶佢返大陸岩啲"},{"pid":"64110ade9dd79309ad12b831f9ec074d7b4f7c3d","tid":321650,"uid":96107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同年紀大啲既親戚去都預左比佢地嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本又嫌 台灣又嫌 東南亞又嫌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我學醒左 帶佢地玩啲大陸三日兩夜果啲團 佢地反而玩得好開心<br />\n<br />\n不過家人都唔係問題 如果預著同另一半個旅行方式唔岩仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同老母講之前上網睇到話日本人都唔多鍾意香港遊客 我老母話咩咁咪好似啲香港人會歧視啲內地同胞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係帶佢返大陸岩啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次同老母去京阪 又嫌日本無野睇 又嫌間酒店貴 又嫌啲野食唔岩口味 真係頭到大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以都係無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02da752f7b1a5bbef5e33562c5feccb429e9cf50","tid":321650,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:34:20.000Z","msg":"嫌酒店貴個啲家人一定係未開發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對旅行冇乜sense<br />\n比得少又嫌細都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed02a235bb398351c5a09e1bba20f50fabef0d82","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T10:52:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同年紀大啲既親戚去都預左比佢地嫌三嫌四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去日本又嫌 台灣又嫌 東南亞又嫌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我學醒左 帶佢地玩啲大陸三日兩夜果啲團 佢地反而玩得好開心<br />\n<br />\n不過家人都唔係問題 如果預著同另一半個旅行方式唔岩仲慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同老母講之前上網睇到話日本人都唔多鍾意香港遊客 我老母話咩咁咪好似啲香港人會歧視啲內地同胞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係帶佢返大陸岩啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上次同老母去京阪 又嫌日本無野睇 又嫌間酒店貴 又嫌啲野食唔岩口味 真係頭到大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以都係無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母話覺得日本同香港差唔多喎 話覺得香港街道乾淨過日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4faf64210bcddf671210b37387a09e686a931add","tid":321650,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:01:49.000Z","msg":"照相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主大陸岀世？"},{"pid":"82e6ef4bcd55aa695cb1c0bc27efa7c0c127fa5d","tid":321650,"uid":32927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>照相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主大陸岀世？</blockquote><br />\nSorry打錯"},{"pid":"1f48736fa050fb7a3f4615f4623396161c76317f","tid":321650,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:10:42.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"195f2533c89c485f16f068fd342770ae251e93c0","tid":321650,"uid":65142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T11:16:56.000Z","msg":"屌講起就一肚火<br />\n識左6,7年 平時出街都冇乜野一直都好fd<br />\n我屌 一去旅行就見哂真章<br />\n度縮到仆街 成撚日計埋哂啲婆乸數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a